---
source: tests/snapshots.rs
expression: buffer_to_string(&buf)
---
lazyjust  —  justfile: ./justfile ▾        ? help  q quit                       
┌ recipes ─────────────────┐┌ preview ─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│>GR┌help──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│   │▸ List focus                                                          │   │
│   │    j / k, ↓ / ↑          move cursor within recipes list             │   │
│   │    h / l, ← / →          cycle through the recipe's previous run     │   │
│   │sessions                                                              │   │
│   │    Enter                 run recipe — if a session is already running│   │
│   │for it, jump there                                                    │   │
│   │    Shift+Enter / r       always spawn a new session (never reuse)    │   │
│   │    /                     enter fuzzy-filter mode                     │   │
│   │    d                     open justfile-switcher dropdown             │   │
│   │    Tab                   cycle focus between list and session pane   │   │
│   │    K                     kill the focused session (confirms)         │   │
│   │    x                     close the focused session (confirms)        │   │
│   │    Ctrl+o / Ctrl+i       jump to next / previous session with unread │   │
│   │output                                                                │   │
│   │    L                     copy the focused session's log path         │   │
│   │    > / < / =             grow / shrink / reset the left pane width   │   │
│   │    F1 / ?                open this help                              │   │
│   │    e                     open the startup-errors modal               │   │
│   │    q                     quit — confirms if sessions are running     │   │
│   │                                                                      │   │
│   │  Session focus                                                       │   │
│   │    F12 / Ctrl+g          return focus to the recipes list            │   │
│   │    PgUp / PgDn           scroll session output up / down             │   │
│   │    Home / End            jump to top / bottom of scrollback          │   │
│   └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
└──────────────────────────┘└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
Help — Esc / q to close                                                         

